<div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Roche_limit_(ring).PNG" class="image" title="The varying orbital speed of the material eventually causes it to form a ring."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3f/Roche_limit_%28ring%29.PNG" width="300" height="122" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">The varying orbital speed of the material eventually causes it to form a ring.</div>
</div>
